{"pageNumber":535,"juzNumber":27,"verses":[{"key":"56:17","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":17,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"يَطُوفُ عَلَيْهِمْ وِلْدَٰنٌۭ مُّخَلَّدُونَ","translationText":"There will circulate among them young boys made eternal"},{"key":"56:18","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":18,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"بِأَكْوَابٍۢ وَأَبَارِيقَ وَكَأْسٍۢ مِّن مَّعِينٍۢ","translationText":"With vessels, pitchers and a cup [of wine] from a flowing spring -"},{"key":"56:19","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":19,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"لَّا يُصَدَّعُونَ عَنْهَا وَلَا يُنزِفُونَ","translationText":"No headache will they have therefrom, nor will they be intoxicated -"},{"key":"56:20","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":20,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَفَٰكِهَةٍۢ مِّمَّا يَتَخَيَّرُونَ","translationText":"And fruit of what they select"},{"key":"56:21","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":21,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَلَحْمِ طَيْرٍۢ مِّمَّا يَشْتَهُونَ","translationText":"And the meat of fowl, from whatever they desire."},{"key":"56:22","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":22,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَحُورٌ عِينٌۭ","translationText":"And [for them are] fair women with large, [beautiful] eyes,"},{"key":"56:23","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":23,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"كَأَمْثَٰلِ ٱللُّؤْلُؤِ ٱلْمَكْنُونِ","translationText":"The likenesses of pearls well-protected,"},{"key":"56:24","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":24,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"جَزَآءًۢ بِمَا كَانُوا۟ يَعْمَلُونَ","translationText":"As reward for what they used to do."},{"key":"56:25","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":25,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"لَا يَسْمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغْوًۭا وَلَا تَأْثِيمًا","translationText":"They will not hear therein ill speech or commission of sin -"},{"key":"56:26","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":26,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"إِلَّا قِيلًۭا سَلَٰمًۭا سَلَٰمًۭا","translationText":"Only a saying: \"Peace, peace.\""},{"key":"56:27","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":27,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَأَصْحَٰبُ ٱلْيَمِينِ مَآ أَصْحَٰبُ ٱلْيَمِينِ","translationText":"The companions of the right - what are the companions of the right?"},{"key":"56:28","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":28,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"فِى سِدْرٍۢ مَّخْضُودٍۢ","translationText":"[They will be] among lote trees with thorns removed"},{"key":"56:29","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":29,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَطَلْحٍۢ مَّنضُودٍۢ","translationText":"And [banana] trees layered [with fruit]"},{"key":"56:30","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":30,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَظِلٍّۢ مَّمْدُودٍۢ","translationText":"And shade extended"},{"key":"56:31","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":31,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَمَآءٍۢ مَّسْكُوبٍۢ","translationText":"And water poured out"},{"key":"56:32","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":32,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَفَٰكِهَةٍۢ كَثِيرَةٍۢ","translationText":"And fruit, abundant [and varied],"},{"key":"56:33","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":33,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"لَّا مَقْطُوعَةٍۢ وَلَا مَمْنُوعَةٍۢ","translationText":"Neither limited [to season] nor forbidden,"},{"key":"56:34","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":34,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَفُرُشٍۢ مَّرْفُوعَةٍ","translationText":"And [upon] beds raised high."},{"key":"56:35","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":35,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"إِنَّآ أَنشَأْنَٰهُنَّ إِنشَآءًۭ","translationText":"Indeed, We have produced the women of Paradise in a [new] creation"},{"key":"56:36","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":36,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"فَجَعَلْنَٰهُنَّ أَبْكَارًا","translationText":"And made them virgins,"},{"key":"56:37","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":37,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"عُرُبًا أَتْرَابًۭا","translationText":"Devoted [to their husbands] and of equal age,"},{"key":"56:38","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":38,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"لِّأَصْحَٰبِ ٱلْيَمِينِ","translationText":"For the companions of the right [who are]"},{"key":"56:39","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":39,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"ثُلَّةٌۭ مِّنَ ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","translationText":"A company of the former peoples"},{"key":"56:40","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":40,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَثُلَّةٌۭ مِّنَ ٱلْءَاخِرِينَ","translationText":"And a company of the later peoples."},{"key":"56:41","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":41,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَأَصْحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ مَآ أَصْحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ","translationText":"And the companions of the left - what are the companions of the left?"},{"key":"56:42","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":42,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"فِى سَمُومٍۢ وَحَمِيمٍۢ","translationText":"[They will be] in scorching fire and scalding water"},{"key":"56:43","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":43,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَظِلٍّۢ مِّن يَحْمُومٍۢ","translationText":"And a shade of black smoke,"},{"key":"56:44","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":44,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"لَّا بَارِدٍۢ وَلَا كَرِيمٍ","translationText":"Neither cool nor beneficial."},{"key":"56:45","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":45,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"إِنَّهُمْ كَانُوا۟ قَبْلَ ذَٰلِكَ مُتْرَفِينَ","translationText":"Indeed they were, before that, indulging in affluence,"},{"key":"56:46","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":46,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَكَانُوا۟ يُصِرُّونَ عَلَى ٱلْحِنثِ ٱلْعَظِيمِ","translationText":"And they used to persist in the great violation,"},{"key":"56:47","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":47,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"وَكَانُوا۟ يَقُولُونَ أَئِذَا مِتْنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابًۭا وَعِظَٰمًا أَءِنَّا لَمَبْعُوثُونَ","translationText":"And they used to say, \"When we die and become dust and bones, are we indeed to be resurrected?"},{"key":"56:48","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":48,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"أَوَءَابَآؤُنَا ٱلْأَوَّلُونَ","translationText":"And our forefathers [as well]?\""},{"key":"56:49","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":49,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"قُلْ إِنَّ ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ وَٱلْءَاخِرِينَ","translationText":"Say, [O Muhammad], \"Indeed, the former and the later peoples"},{"key":"56:50","surahNumber":56,"ayahNumber":50,"juzNumber":27,"pageNumber":535,"arabicText":"لَمَجْمُوعُونَ إِلَىٰ مِيقَٰتِ يَوْمٍۢ مَّعْلُومٍۢ","translationText":"Are to be gathered together for the appointment of a known Day.\""}],"translationEditionUsed":"en.sahih"}